1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:19,820
Legend of Awakening

3
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,579
Episode 25

4
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,720
You save Su Tang for me.

5
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:28,440
I can save myself with confidence.

6
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,000
Okay.

7
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,240
I promise you.

8
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,000
Mr. Lu.

9
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:39,520
I’d like to go with you to rescue Miss Su Tang.

10
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,160
Ziyan.

11
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,000
You…

12
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:44,440
You have been taking care of me.

13
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,640
I regard you as my family.

14
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,420
Mr. Lu. If you still regard me as a friend,

15
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,440
don’t keep me out of this.

16
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,120
Fine.

17
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:57,120
More people, more assurance.

18
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:00,160
Okay.

19
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:04,360
I entrust Su Tang’s life to you.

20
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,280
What?

21
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,600
The Big Dipper even broke into the jail
and rescued Lu Ping.

22
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,720
Now how can Qin Qi take him back to

23
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:21,120
E’zhou for execution?

24
00:03:25,040 --> 00:03:25,600
Yes.

25
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,400
It was you who proposed to the master that you’d

26
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,920
rob Lu Ping from the path under the mountain.

27
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,100
Now you are one step behind Qin Qi.

28
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:40,000
I don’t know how Mr. Xu will explain to master.

29
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,000
I need more time

30
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,000
to change the situation here.

31
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:57,180
[Bring Xu Weifeng back now.
Don’t disturb Big Dipper.]

32
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,580
I don’t think you have the chance.

33
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,920
Master wants to meet you.

34
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:16,800
General Qin.

35
00:04:17,829 --> 00:04:18,360
Open the door.

36
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:18,880
Yes.

37
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:41,360
When are you going to cut off my head?

38
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,880
At noon tomorrow.

39
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,240
This is an explanation to Tan

40
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,540
to comfort Xu Tianbing’s spirit.

41
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:52,080
Okay.

42
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:55,360
I still have time to have a dream.

43
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,159
How could you

44
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,250
fall asleep now?

45
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:15,880
Lu Ping.

46
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,240
You must hate me.

47
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,690
I can only live until tomorrow.

48
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,640
Why should I hate you?

49
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:29,450
In Kaifeng, you were supposed to be

50
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:32,040
the winner of the Force Combat Convention.

51
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,680
But you were framed by me.

52
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,800
You saved me

53
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,920
in E’zhou.

54
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:40,730
But you are still being charged for me.

55
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,840
I’ve sacrificed you several times.

56
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,060
You have reason

57
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,960
to hate me.

58
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,570
You and I have different needs.

59
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,440
You did it for Qin Family,

60
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,120
and Shuo.

61
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,320
I did it for

62
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,280
a clear conscience.

63
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,120
I will do it again

64
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,880
for the people

65
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,360
I care.

66
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,000
In this case,

67
00:06:29,960 --> 00:06:31,360
I have nothing to regret.

68
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,460
You are a talented person.

69
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,120
If I knew you earlier,

70
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,840
I would have taken you under my command

71
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,040
at all costs.

72
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:44,040
But it’s too late

73
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,180
to say that.

74
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,840
Lu Ping.

75
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,760
I’m sorry for you.

76
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:02,200
I will repay you in my next life.

77
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,240
Get ready for tomorrow.

78
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,480
Master.

79
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,960
Master Zhou was defeated by Yan Qiuci that day.

80
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,890
We have not found his whereabouts.

81
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,520
Mr. Xu.

82
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:49,480
Your plan failed.

83
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,280
Mr. Xu.

84
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,900
Don’t do things

85
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:55,040
beyond your ability.

86
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,960
Or you’ll get everyone in trouble.

87
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,159
Am I right?

88
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:02,560
Master.

89
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:05,280
He is useless now,

90
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:07,520
and he knows the secrets of our gang.

91
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,540
It’s better

92
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,040
to get rid of him.

93
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,200
Wait.

94
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,640
Master.

95
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:15,120
I have an idea.

96
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,480
You want Lu Ping alive.

97
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,280
Right?

98
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,440
You know too much.

99
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,180
I could bring him back.

100
00:08:23,960 --> 00:08:24,440
Master.

101
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,090
You won’t trust this man again.

102
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,520
If you want Lu Ping alive.

103
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,060
I can take him back.

104
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,840
Lu Ping will be executed tomorrow.

105
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,640
Qin Qi will be strictly guarded.

106
00:08:35,909 --> 00:08:37,760
Now Master Zhou hasn’t come back.

107
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:38,960
Yan Xifan is too obvious.

108
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,830
You’ve no ideal person to take over the job.

109
00:08:40,830 --> 00:08:41,549
I am the only one

110
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:43,240
to bring Lu Ping back

111
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,840
without being seen.

112
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:54,840
Tonight at the ferry,

113
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,440
I’ll wait for you until 1 a.m.

114
00:08:58,800 --> 00:08:59,320
Okay.

115
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:20,340
[Breeze Mansion]

116
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,480
It’s hard to break through.

117
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:19,080
We’ll only alarm the guards.

118
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,760
Could you sneak in?

119
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,160
The scope is too large.

120
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:25,480
If we can’t confirm the position of Miss Su Tang,

121
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,280
I’m afraid that I will alarm the guards.

122
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,280
We can’t afford to

123
00:09:28,760 --> 00:09:29,840
alarm the guards.

124
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:35,040
Xu Weifeng hasn’t been back for a long time.

125
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:37,100
Has he sent Su Tang out of the mansion?

126
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,280
What can we do?

127
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,930
Don’t worry.

128
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:15,560
I’ve been checking his gate for the past two days.

129
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:18,140
I haven’t closed my eyes for a moment.

130
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,200
I swear in the name of

131
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,520
the World’s No. 1 Assassin that

132
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:22,440
Su Tang

133
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,410
is still in his mansion.

134
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,500
Xu Weifeng did something.

135
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,860
He made a mess of spices

136
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,680
in the mansion.

137
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,620
So I can’t determine the location of Su Tang.

138
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,780
And no one came in or out

139
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:49,720
of these two days

140
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:52,490
carring a vessel that could hold a person.

141
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:55,400
And since he left the post,

142
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:59,120
he has added many guards to the mansion.

143
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:00,560
So

144
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,980
Su Tang must be in the mansion.

145
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:06,170
Lu Ping will be executed at noon tomorrow.

146
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,640
If he has ambition,

147
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,720
he would leave tomorrow.

148
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:12,000
It’s the only chance for us to save Su Tang

149
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,880
when he leaves.

150
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:17,320
So whether there’s a clue of Su Tang or not,

151
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,330
we need to break in the mansion.

152
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:30,800
Mo Lin.

153
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,840
How long since you had a good meal

154
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,240
and slept?

155
00:11:36,640 --> 00:11:37,640
I don’t remember.

156
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,240
As long as you relax a little bit,

157
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:43,240
you may miss the clue.

158
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,080
I will take the shift.

159
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,130
That’s okay.

160
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,440
It’s about the life of my master.

161
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:52,280
I can do it.

162
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,880
You’re going to die first.

163
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,720
I know you honor your master.

164
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,720
She is not only my master.

165
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:02,880
She is Su Tang.

166
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,040
As long as she’s safe,

167
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,000
even if I die,

168
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,420
it doesn't matter.

169
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:22,620
[Breeze Mansion]

170
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,560
Bao Niang.

171
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:34,480
Mister.

172
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,490
I told you many times

173
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:39,420
you don’t need to clean the study.

174
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,800
You can leave now.

175
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:41,760
Mister.

176
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,720
You seem to be getting cranky lately.

177
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:45,760
Bao Niang.

178
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:48,160
I saved your life.

179
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:49,760
Just follow my order.

180
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,800
Okay?

181
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,120
Yes.

182
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,440
Hold it.

183
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,960
People smell from their skin.

184
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,680
I use the silver needle to stimulate the acupoint,

185
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:32,810
which can temporarily seal the smell,

186
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,560
so no one can find you.

187
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:38,200
I will be gentle.

188
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,000
I have candy for you,

189
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,440
if you feel hurt.

190
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,800
How about my brother?

191
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,400
Su Tang.

192
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,800
Is Lu Ping important

193
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,760
to Shanhai Gang?

194
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:10,600
What do you want from my brother?

195
00:14:13,400 --> 00:14:15,200
I underestimated Shanhai Gang.

196
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:18,240
I wanted to use them to finish my plan.

197
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,450
But I was controlled

198
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:22,560
by them.

199
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,720
They casted me aside

200
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,440
like an old shoe.

201
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:28,840
Answer me.

202
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,600
What do you want from my brother?

203
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,320
Didn’t you tell me

204
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,880
not to give up dream?

205
00:14:41,040 --> 00:14:43,840
Since Lu Ping is so important to Shanhai Gang.

206
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:47,000
Then only when I get Lu Ping first

207
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:50,720
can Shanhai Gang help me willingly.

208
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,320
Am I right?

209
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:58,440
Xu Weifeng.

210
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,760
You can kill me.

211
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,120
Don’t hurt my brother.

212
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:30,880
How could I hurt you?

213
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:33,810
No matter what happened to Lu Ping,

214
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:36,220
I will take good care of you for him

215
00:15:37,440 --> 00:15:38,970
and will not hurt you again.

216
00:16:11,080 --> 00:16:12,680
The smell can be sealed,

217
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:15,890
but the smell of blood can’t be sealed.

218
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:20,000
Brother.

219
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,720
I can’t save you this time.

220
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:26,330
I just hope that you won’t be dragged down by me

221
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:29,200
and you can find some way of tiding over the crisis.

222
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:29,880
Mo Lin.

223
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:32,440
Please find me.

224
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:42,360
This man has personal relationship with Qin Qi.

225
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:44,890
I am afraid Qin Qi will find one to replace him.

226
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:47,480
General Xu is from Tan.

227
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:51,640
The murderer should be taken back to Tan by me.

228
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,120
Mr. Xu.

229
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:55,360
I’m afraid it’s out of line.

230
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:01,540
It is the order of the Military Minister, Mr. Xu.

231
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,360
If you dare to violate, you may hinder

232
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,760
the friendship between the two countries.

233
00:17:06,589 --> 00:17:07,760
Yes. Mr. Xu.

234
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:27,640
I’m dying.

235
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:30,840
Can’t I see a face that makes me happy?

236
00:17:31,600 --> 00:17:33,120
Why should I see you?

237
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:35,400
Lu Ping.

238
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,320
I’ve told you

239
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:39,280
I regard you as my friend.

240
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:40,600
Now,

241
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:42,760
Qin Qi is going to kill you.

242
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:45,360
I am coming to save you.

243
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:14,100
[Breeze Mansion]

244
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,040
Mo Lin.

245
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:28,440
Ziyan will distract the guards later.

246
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:29,900
You and I go to the mansion.

247
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:32,740
I will guard and you go to find Su Tang.

248
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:35,000
We leave the rest to god.

249
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,810
I don’t believe the god.

250
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,700
I only believe Su Tang.

251
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:40,400
She is my master.

252
00:18:41,080 --> 00:18:42,810
She must have a way to notice us.

253
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:51,360
Ziyan won’t have much time.

254
00:18:51,520 --> 00:18:52,680
Let’s split up.

255
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:57,880
Blood.

256
00:18:58,880 --> 00:19:00,480
The smell of Su Tang’s blood.

257
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:02,680
I know where she is.

258
00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:52,200
Master.

259
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:53,700
I am coming for you.

260
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:56,800
Master.

261
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:57,880
You…

262
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:12,920
Master.

263
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,160
Master.

264
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,280
Master. Are you okay?

265
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:20,640
I will stop the bleeding.

266
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,160
Thanks.

267
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:30,880
Master.

268
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:31,640
Master.

269
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:32,960
Are you okay?

270
00:20:57,400 --> 00:21:00,200
As you said, you practiced.

271
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:03,680
Shanhai Gang likes to have a partner like you.

272
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,400
Senior Xu.

273
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:08,760
I thought you have huge ambition.

274
00:21:10,080 --> 00:21:12,240
You are a running dog of Shanhai Gang.

275
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,400
I brought Lu Ping here.

276
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,400
I want it to be the same as before.

277
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,640
Shanhai Gang and Tan work together
to eliminate Shuo.

278
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:24,880
Otherwise,

279
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:28,360
even if I should kill him,

280
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,480
I won’t let Shanhai Gang success.

281
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:37,440
Okay.

282
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:38,960
I promise you.

283
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:49,360
This Shanhai Token shows my promise.

284
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,420
When I return to Shanhai Gang,

285
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:53,240
I will plan this.

286
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:55,640
Deal.

287
00:21:59,040 --> 00:21:59,840
