578
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,440
Miss Ling, don’t get me wrong.

579
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:47,240
I don’t care about the reputation given by others.

580
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:48,720
You are my best friend

581
00:36:49,160 --> 00:36:51,320
in my heart.

582
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,640
I am glad to

583
00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:55,640
see you back in one piece.

584
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:56,600
Really?

585
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:59,380
I am telling the truth.

586
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:00,720
Now.

587
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:03,720
You’re no longer a maid.

588
00:37:04,160 --> 00:37:06,420
