589
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:09,880
Since you have said that we are friends,

590
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:12,040
then I saw that my friend was in trouble,

591
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:13,970
so I should help to take care of him.

592
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:25,580
[Peace and Prosperity]

593
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:18,400
What’s that?

594
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,840
I am glad to

595
00:37:24,160 --> 00:37:26,160
see you back from Shanhai Gang safe.

596
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:27,360
In my hometown,

597
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:29,880
the people who come back from the disaster

598
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:30,960
have to cross the fire pot and stick peach branches

599
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:32,960
to dispel ghosts and evil spirits.

600
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,240
