601
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:39,960
No.

602
00:37:41,160 --> 00:37:42,560
I think it’s good.

603
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:52,600
I wish you peace and prosperity

604
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,480
in your life.

605
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:03,800
May you have

606
00:38:04,960 --> 00:38:06,290
a bright and happy life.

607
00:38:19,100 --> 00:38:21,860
[E’zhou Post]

608
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,420
Master Xia.

609
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:34,410
General Qin.

610
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:38,040
I have told his majesty that

611
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:42,280
everything that happened recently was

612
00:38:42,560 --> 00:38:44,220
because of my rebellious son.

613
00:38:44,600 --> 00:38:46,840
Now the truth is out.

614
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:49,320
His majesty still hopes to have peace

615
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:51,880
with Shuo forever.

616
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:53,480
That is wise.

617
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:55,600
It’s really the blessing of Tan.

618
00:38:57,640 --> 00:39:00,400
Your son is really cunning.

619
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:03,080
I’m afraid we would be under control

620
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:05,400
by him and Shanhai Gang.

621
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:07,400
if we hadn’t taken the move.

622
00:39:08,240 --> 00:39:11,040
Thanks to the two young heroes,

623
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:13,160
Lu Ping and Xifan,

624
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:15,320
this matter can be solved smoothly.

625
00:39:15,440 --> 00:39:17,680
If two of them didn’t work together,

626
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:19,560
I don’t know how my son

627
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:22,720
will do irreparable sin.

628
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:25,080
Compared with them,

629
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:27,680
I’m really ashamed.

630
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:30,290
I’m not good at teaching children.

631
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,460
When the peace talks are over,

632
00:39:32,720 --> 00:39:35,800
I will make a plea to his majesty.

633
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:39,540
Master Xia was not polite.

634
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:42,720
I hope it didn’t bother you.

635
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,480
You cherish the country,

636
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:47,320
and protect the people.

637
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:49,120
I admire you.

638
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:50,920
As for your son.

639
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:53,200
I am sorry for your loss.

640
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:57,320
Thanks, General Qin.

641
00:39:58,520 --> 00:40:00,520
Now that the document has been exchanged,

642
00:40:00,520 --> 00:40:02,280
I will order the Longjie Army

643
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:04,560
to leave your country as soon as possible.

644
00:40:04,560 --> 00:40:05,760
I will also tell his majesty

645
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,760
to release the prisoners as soon as possible.

646
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:10,920
You can also let your subordinates

647
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:12,160
open the gate to settle the refugees.

648
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:14,120
General Qin has arranged it properly.

649
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:16,000
I am willing to help.

650
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:20,000
Yan Xifan had the crime of conspiracy,

651
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:23,080
but he was under control of Shanhai Gang’s cult.

652
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:25,920
He didn’t kill General Xu.

653
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:28,920
Besides, he made up for it later.

654
00:40:29,600 --> 00:40:31,920
I hope Tan will forgive him.

655
00:40:34,080 --> 00:40:35,410
Yan Jin and Shanhai Gang

656
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:38,400
had done countless crimes in Shuo.

657
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:41,640
His majesty wishes to remand him to Kaifeng
for trial.

658
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:43,120
His majesty has ordered that all matters concerning

659
00:40:43,120 --> 00:40:44,580
the Shanhai Gang be handed

660
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:46,360
over to your country.

661
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:48,280
General Qin, please.

662
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:50,960
Thanks, minister.

663
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:01,300
How is everything?

664
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:04,480
The gate will be reopened in two hours.

665
00:41:06,680 --> 00:41:07,360
Thanks.

666
00:41:08,520 --> 00:41:09,080
Lu Ping.

667
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:11,720
You have made great contributions this time.

668
00:41:11,720 --> 00:41:14,800
Do you only want to open the gate early?

669
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:17,060
Don’t you ask anything for yourself?

670
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:18,560
A high official with a high salary.

671
00:41:18,560 --> 00:41:19,490
A fancy mansion.

672
00:41:19,680 --> 00:41:20,740
As long as you want,

673
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:22,520
I can report to his majesty

674
00:41:22,720 --> 00:41:24,320
and try my best to help you.

675
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:30,080
I’m free

676
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,920
and well fed now.

677
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:34,890
What do I want these things for?

678
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,840
I’ve protected the people in this city

679
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,960
from the plot of Shanhai Gang.

680
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:42,060
Watching them go back home

681
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:43,840
and have a peaceful life.

682
00:41:46,240 --> 00:41:47,440
I am happy.

683
00:41:50,200 --> 00:41:51,800
After the peace talks between the two countries,

684
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:53,200
Minister Xu will hold

685
00:41:53,400 --> 00:41:55,280
several celebrations in the city.

686
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:58,340
At that time, people will go out to celebrate together.

687
00:41:58,400 --> 00:41:59,560
I suggest you

688
00:42:00,040 --> 00:42:01,040
go and have a look.

689
00:42:01,600 --> 00:42:02,560
Go and see

690
00:42:02,680 --> 00:42:04,560
the city and

691
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:06,600
those people you are trying to protect.

692
00:42:06,600 --> 00:42:07,660
That would be fine.

693
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:09,200
But

694
00:42:10,080 --> 00:42:11,480
