695
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:13,000
if I go alone.

696
00:42:13,720 --> 00:42:15,180
Can I take Qin Sang with me?

697
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,280
She likes the celebration.

698
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:17,280
She must be happy.

699
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,320
You can go alone.

700
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,500
Don’t bring Qin Sang with you.

701
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:24,400
She is a Miss in Qin Family.

702
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:25,960
She is a young lady of a noble family.

703
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:27,690
How could she hang out with you?

704
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,640
Qin Sang wanders all day.

705
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,920
-How could you say that?
-You…

706
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,800
Do whatever I say.

707
00:42:37,320 --> 00:42:38,850
It’s none of your business.

708
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:41,080
Didn’t you let me ask anything for myself?

709
00:42:41,080 --> 00:42:42,000
I want this.

710
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:43,130
I am telling you,

711
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:46,000
I’ll trade my previous credit for Qin Sang

712
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:47,560
to accompany me out.

713
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,370
If you are worried about us,

714
00:42:49,640 --> 00:42:50,500
you can follow.

715
00:42:50,640 --> 00:42:52,440
I’m the leader of the Longjie Army.

716
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:54,240
I have many military affairs to deal with.

717
00:42:54,240 --> 00:42:55,500
How can I idle with you?

718
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:57,760
Right.

719
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,600
You can’t do anything

720
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:01,240
if you let Qin Sang by your side.

721
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:01,760
You…

722
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:06,960
Fine.

723
00:43:07,920 --> 00:43:09,440
For your credit,

724
00:43:11,040 --> 00:43:11,900
just this time.

725
00:43:12,040 --> 00:43:12,840
That’s great.

726
00:43:13,040 --> 00:43:14,370
Thank you, General Qin.

727
00:43:15,520 --> 00:43:16,360
Come out.

728
00:43:16,720 --> 00:43:17,680
He agreed.

729
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:21,960
I have the best brother in the world.

